query:
SELECT
                id,
                user_id,
                event_type::text AS "event_type!",
                CASE
                    WHEN risk_score < 33 THEN 'low'
                    WHEN risk_score < 66 THEN 'medium'
                    ELSE 'high'
                END AS "severity!",
                ip_address::text AS "ip_address",
                user_agent,
                details,
                created_at
            FROM security_audit_log
            WHERE user_id = $1
            ORDER BY created_at DESC
            LIMIT $2
